OL,3,CThousands of drivers wrongly fined for
OL,4,Cspeeding since 2021 due to faulty
OL,5,Ccameras
OL,7,FThe agency said it had identified
OL,8,Faround 2,650 incorrect camera
OL,9,Factivations since 2021, less than two
OL,10,Fa day.
OL,12,FNot all of those will have resulted in
OL,13,Ffines as camera activations are not
OL,14,Falways enforced, and the total amounts
OL,15,Fto less than 0.1% of the 6 million
OL,16,Factivations in the same period.
