OL,3,CThousands of drivers wrongly fined for
OL,4,Cspeeding since 2021 due to faulty
OL,5,Ccameras
OL,7,FThe issue affected 10% of motorways
OL,8,Fand A roads in England, and National
OL,9,FHighways is working to implement a
OL,10,Fsolution to the problem as soon as
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,FAnyone who has been incorrectly fined
OL,14,Fwill be contacted directly by the
OL,15,Fpolice, the agency said, with fines
OL,16,Freimbursed and any points removed from
OL,17,Ftheir licence.
