OL,7,FNational Highways chief executive Nick
OL,8,FHarris said: "Safety is our number one
OL,9,Fpriority and we have developed a fix
OL,10,Ffor this technical anomaly to maintain
OL,11,Fthe highest levels of safety on these
OL,12,Froads and make sure no one is wrongly
OL,13,Fprosecuted."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,16,FTransport said: "We apologise to
OL,17,Fanyone who has been affected. Safety
OL,18,Fwas never compromised, and we are
OL,19,Fworking with policing to ensure nobody
OL,20,Fis incorrectly prosecuted in future.
